divs: Sighting DetailsI saw this blinking light , I thought maybe it was a star but it seemed to be too low to be a star , so I waited to see if it was a plane waiting in a path to land . But after 10 minutes it didn't move . It seems to be pulsating different colors of light . It definitely is under the plane patterns .
